      • getChangeSetUrl

        public String getChangeSetUrl()
        The SVN or GIT URL that will be used to synchronize user profiles and changesets for this bundle. With SSH urls, such as "ssh://someuser@csfe.aceworkspace.net..." the contents between 'ssh://' and '@' will be replaced with the currently logged in user's syncUserName - as specified in that users profile.
        Returns:
        possible object is String
